  <item>
    <title>PhD &amp; postdoc positions at ZMT in ecology, microbiology and sociology</title>
    <link>http://plus.pacenet.eu/funding/phd-postdoc-positions-zmt-ecology-microbiology-and-sociology</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/partners/zmt&quot;&gt;The Leibniz Centre for Tropical Marine Ecology (&lt;abbr title=&quot;Leibniz Centre for Tropical Marine Ecology&quot;&gt;ZMT&lt;/abbr&gt;)&lt;/a&gt; currently has a number of openings for early career researchers. Here are a few of them:&lt;/p&gt;
